 on Sunday “in full alignment with the recommendations indicated by our authorities.” In regard to production, the company will begin reducing its operations “to a minimum … with the sole purpose of avoiding irreversible effects that could make it impossible to reactivate our economic activity.” So far, Mexico has registered 1,510 confirmed cases of COVID-19 and 50 deaths related to the disease NY Post Vanguard Heineken premium beer is the international beer brand that has made its way around the world. March 28, 2010 In "Business" Heineken premium beer is the great beer brand that has made its way around the world. The Dutch lager was first brewed by the Heineken family in 1864 when Adriaan Heineken convinced his mother that there would be fewer problems with alcoholism in Holland if the Dutch could be induced… May 29, 2016 In "Business" Dutch brewing giant Heineken on Monday saw its share price plummet over five percent after revising outlook downwards for the year, despite reporting a leap in first half profits. July 30, 2018 In "Business"